		<article class="post-7249 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-allposts category-sciencetechnology tag-cognition tag-dream tag-engineering tag-manipulation tag-memory tag-mit tag-neuroscience tag-science tag-sleep tag-technology post-listing">
			
			<div class="post-inner">
				<h1 class="name post-title entry-title" itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Thing"><span itemprop="name">Neuroscientists successfully control dreams of rats. Could humans be next?</span></h1>

				
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="share-post">
